snippet.title: Cash Cleaner Simulator - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cash Cleaner Simulator is a chill first-person simulator where you become a money laundering pro... 
but with a twist! Cash is LITERALLY dirty!

Find satisfaction in the transformation.  We're talking dirty bills turning into crisp stacks, stacks becoming brick-like bundles, and those bundles – boom! – building a freakin' cash pyramid!  Who needs banks? Or, hey, maybe you're more of a "burn baby burn" kinda player – that works too!

Wash it, dry it, clean it, stack it, band it, bag it, and deliver that sweet, sweet, fresh-faced cash!

💸 Add to your wishlist on Steam! 💸
